
There are two different ICON License contracts for non-commercial research purposes, see the directory "license":

(1) An individual license is available with the code and via a web-based platform managed by MPI-M, see: MPI-M-ICONLizenzvertragV143.pdf
(2) An institutional license (for a whole research institute) is available from DWD, see: DWD-ICON_Non-Commercial_Research_Licence.pdf

Software to which a separate license is applicable is subject to the terms of its associated license, see files in the according directory 
"Third_party_license_terms" in the subdirectory "license".

MPI for Meteorology, Hamburg, 2018-11-27, R. Budich
